{"tid":1087993,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［拋磚引玉］入嚟講個家常小故事","createTime":"2019-04-01T17:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T18:12:00.000Z","uid":138740,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6e6ac16f2276a1eb60d9685aef698ae09d39fe09","tid":1087993,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:04:56.000Z","msg":"呀明係個啱啱20歲嘅連登仔，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家留低你&lsquo;朋友&rsquo;嘅故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3682b57ec14921294cad4f74eca8cb970125ca","tid":1087993,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:17:16.000Z","msg":"從前有個小朋友 ，佢講大話。有一日，佢死咗。"},{"pid":"85d8c66299fb3baed9ac58b45e96b6c2a1f2cc93","tid":1087993,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca3682b57ec14921294cad4f74eca8cb970125ca","tid":1087993,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:17:16.000Z","msg":"從前有個小朋友 ，佢講大話。有一日，佢死咗。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:30:11.000Z","msg":"睇唔明有咩含意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af018d8ef890f9e2e9e177d26beb5a81c94fc53","tid":1087993,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:40:01.000Z","msg":"從前有座山，山上有座廟，廟入邊住咗兩個和尚；<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"javascript\">(()=&gt;{\n while(1){\n  console.log(&quot;從前有座山，山上有座廟，廟入邊住咗兩個和尚；\\n有一日，大和尚就同小和尚講：&quot;)\n }\n})();</code></pre>"},{"pid":"23fca712ea4223aaa8a622e56e7992641fa29b1f","tid":1087993,"uid":153496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T18:12:00.000Z","msg":"話說有個農夫苦於旱災，收成唔好，決定搵個算命佬求雨。算命佬揸住支毛筆，好凝重咁喺一張黃紙到寫咗啲野，再將張紙放入一個錦囊到，交畀農夫，吩咐農夫要等到落雨天先可以打開個錦囊睇。<br />\n卒之有日，天降甘露，農夫興高采烈打開錦囊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張黃紙寫住「今日有雨」。"}]}